seo: spiderflow,远程命令执行漏洞,插件,检测
seo_en: spiderflow, remote command execute vulnerability, plugin, detection
summary: 该插件用于检测SpiderFlow应用是否存在远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定的POST请求并利用DNSLog验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the SpiderFlow application has a remote command execution vulnerability by sending a specific POST request and using DNSLog to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
